<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />

    <title>Main page</title>
    <script src="/js/home/index.js" defer></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body style="background-color: #f8f9fa">
    <%- include ('../layouts/header') %>

    <div class="main4Img">
      <div class="container input-group mb-2 Likethings-containers">
        <div class="container Likethings-items">
          <h4>당신에게 맞는 숙소를 정해봅시다!</h4>
          <button>
            <a href="/quest %>">찾아보기</a>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h4>어떤 숙소를 찾고 계신가요?</h4>
      <div class="main4Img-container">
        <% for (var i = 0; i < data.length; i++) { %>
        <div class="main4Img-item1">
          <a href="/search?value= + <%= data[i].c %>">
            <div class="changeBox"></div>
          </a>
          <div class="main4Img-text">
            <img src="image/mainImg<%=i+1%>.jpg" class="main4Img-img" />
            <div class="main4Img-img-text">
              <h4><%= data[i].a %></h4>
              <p><%= data[i].b %></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% }%>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
